name: DarkBASIC Object
summary: Learn about .DBO files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: To create a DBO file, select "Export" from the File menu within DarkBASIC. Then choose "Dark Basic Object (*.dbo)" as the file type.

description: Program object created with DarkBASIC Pro, a development program for creating 3D games, slideshows, and other applications; developed using the BASIC programming language; may include game levels, 3D models, textures, and other related data.
